&lt;li&gt;Work closely with custom development team to establish feasibility and develop effective custom proposals for simple pack size customization, private label, and more complex custom development deals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow effective sales process within CRM to maximize close rate and drive strong revenue growth within the territory; conduct live QBRs with key clients on a routine basis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain an accurate forecast of both revenue and product demand across the territory&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Respond to RFPs, tenders, write quotations,&amp;nbsp; supply agreements, and other contractual agreements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Co-manage custom projects through to completion through collaboration with customers and Watchmaker’s internal custom team to establish and execute on custom product specifications&lt;/li&gt;
