&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position: &lt;/strong&gt;Senior Director, APAC Sales&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Type: &lt;/strong&gt;Full time&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Department: &lt;/strong&gt;International Sales&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location: &lt;/strong&gt;Singapore, Australia, or US West Coast; domestic and international travel up to 50%&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience: &lt;/strong&gt;Bachelor’s degree required; Master’s preferred.10+ years of experience in life sciences and NGS sales, with multi-country regional management experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an experienced Senior Director, APAC Sales who will play a pivotal role leading and directing all commercial sales efforts across the Asia-Pacific region to maximize revenue and operational excellence. This is an incredible opportunity for someone who is passionate about developing and executing a successful sales strategy for rapid growth across diverse APAC markets. We are looking for candidates with a proven track record of leading multi-country commercial organizations and experience with genomics sales. This role reports to the Chief Commercial Officer.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will thrive in a dynamic, fast-paced working environment and contribute directly to our company culture and success.&amp;nbsp; The candidate will also be a player coach in selling direct to KOL’s and managing a funnel while managing sales reps and distributors in the region.&amp;nbsp; If you possess the following and want to make a meaningful impact, we invite you to explore this role.&lt;/p&gt;
