&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position: &lt;/strong&gt;Technical Marketing Manager or Sr. Technical Marketing Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Type: &lt;/strong&gt;Technical Marketing&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Department: &lt;/strong&gt;Marketing&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location: &lt;/strong&gt;Remote&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience: &lt;/strong&gt;Master’s + 6 years relevant experience; or Bachelor’s + 8 years relevant experience. Experience in biotech and a start-up environment are highly desirable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Watchmaker is inviting applications for the full-time, remote position of Technical Marketing Manager. The successful candidate will thrive in a dynamic, fast-paced working environment and contribute directly to our company culture and success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The position provides an opportunity to develop impactful marketing content, collaborate with cross-functional teams, and drive brand visibility through strategic campaigns, product launches, and industry events.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Simplify complex NGS technical concepts into clear and engaging content that resonates with our audience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the planning, production, and implementation of marketing activities per the strategic plan.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop content for product launch and positioning, including brochures, web landing pages, and FAQs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop content for marketing needs, including long form articles, video scripts, infographics, advertisements, emails, newsletters, and application notes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Draft and edit press releases, blog, and social posts that raise brand awareness.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Research and understand our target audience to produce compelling content, and work with cross-functional teams to align on messaging.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a working understanding of Watchmaker’s product offerings and stay current on applications relevant to Watchmaker’s portfolio.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify relevant industry events and trade shows that present opportunities for brand exposure, lead generation, and networking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support tradeshow attendance by developing show strategy and executing on key deliverables, including the generation of presentations, landing pages, handouts, social, and outreach emails.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
