&lt;li&gt;Strong interpersonal skills and an ability to work as an effective member of a team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good communication and personal task management skills and a high level of self-motivation and initiative.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A creative and disciplined approach to problem-solving.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional writing, editing, and proofreading skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability in developing on-brand messaging that best represents a brand’s voice and tone.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
